title: Ep10: Bi Love Featuring a Bi Couple
itunes:title: Ep10: Bi Love Featuring a Bi Couple
description:
This week's episode of Whoreible Decisions, Weezy and Mandii B sit down with a Bi couple, where both the woman AND man consider themselves bisexual. They discuss how they were able to accept each other, how they met, and how they exist in a society where sexuality is constantly questioned.
